grind the tomatoes as a paste

00:00:23.620 --> 00:00:26.140
sliced onions

00:00:28.380 --> 00:00:30.000
double or heavy cream

00:00:30.385 --> 00:00:32.385
thick greek yogurt

00:00:34.120 --> 00:00:36.120
lemon juice

00:00:36.920 --> 00:00:41.620
my homemade ginger and garlic paste twice, i will tell you  the reason

00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:45.480
my homemade chaat masala

00:00:46.040 --> 00:00:48.040
red chilli powder

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:50.600
garam masala

00:00:50.842 --> 00:00:52.842
coriander powder

00:00:52.842 --> 00:00:54.628
salt

00:00:55.154 --> 00:00:58.934
dry fenugreek leaves

00:00:58.934 --> 00:01:00.280
green chillies

00:01:00.980 --> 00:01:05.020
its a bullet green chillies, its less hot and very good in taste

00:01:05.260 --> 00:01:07.260
cashew nuts

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:10.380
we need oil and ghee

00:01:11.120 --> 00:01:13.780
fresh coriander

00:01:17.340 --> 00:01:20.320
marinate the chicken

00:01:20.320 --> 00:01:21.719
add salt

00:01:24.160 --> 00:01:26.160
red chilli powder

00:01:27.240 --> 00:01:29.240
ginger and garlic paste

00:01:32.109 --> 00:01:35.829
add lemon juice and mix it well

00:01:35.980 --> 00:01:38.700
cover it and put it in the fridge for one hour

00:01:39.120 --> 00:01:47.520
after one hour add the yogurt and mix it again

00:01:48.500 --> 00:01:56.520
in a big pot without the oil put the chicken in it

00:01:57.200 --> 00:02:05.020
cook the chicken on high flame until the chicken's own water gets dry

00:02:05.620 --> 00:02:11.100
you can see, i didn't use water at all its chickens and yogurt water

00:02:11.600 --> 00:02:16.040
dry the water on high flame

00:02:16.460 --> 00:02:19.120
after the chicken cooked, leave it aside

00:02:19.420 --> 00:02:22.540
you need a little oil in the frying pan

00:02:22.947 --> 00:02:24.947
add cashew nuts

00:02:26.820 --> 00:02:33.360
add onions and fry on high flame till onions get in golden

00:02:33.620 --> 00:02:37.480
dont make them too golden

00:02:37.980 --> 00:02:45.340
take out cashew nuts and onions from the frying pan

00:02:45.480 --> 00:02:55.220
after they get in normal temperature, grind them into paste

00:02:55.640 --> 00:03:04.880
i grinded them and made the paste

00:03:11.340 --> 00:03:16.540
in hot ghee add ginger and garlic paste

00:03:16.880 --> 00:03:22.100
fry it on high flame only for 1 to 2 minutes

00:03:22.620 --> 00:03:28.380
turn the flame on medium and add tomatoes paste

00:03:28.760 --> 00:03:32.940
add milk

00:03:34.180 --> 00:03:36.180
add garam masala powder

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:42.740
add coriander powder and mix it with the spoon on medium flame for 4 to 5 minutes

00:03:44.240 --> 00:03:47.140
it will look like this

00:03:53.080 --> 00:03:56.320
add cream

00:04:01.573 --> 00:04:03.573
add chat masala

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:15.160
add the paste of onions and cashew nuts and cook it on medium flame till the ghee come to surface

00:04:15.740 --> 00:04:18.340
ghee came to surface

00:04:18.620 --> 00:04:25.900
add marinated chicken

00:04:34.940 --> 00:04:40.160
add fenugreek leaves

00:04:43.307 --> 00:04:45.307
add green chillies

00:04:46.260 --> 00:04:50.380
mix it and add just little water

00:04:51.300 --> 00:04:57.220
cover it with  a lid and cook it on the medium flame till the ghee come to surface again

00:04:57.728 --> 00:04:59.728
and dry the water

00:05:00.980 --> 00:05:02.980
add water

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:10.780
high the flame, once it's start boiling, turn the flame on low to medium

00:05:11.280 --> 00:05:13.280
cook it till water gets dried

00:05:13.759 --> 00:05:15.759
add fresh coriander, mix it and dish out

